        12/28/2011
    








First to Review
        


This review is more for Dr. Stewart's staff than for him. I am actually a patient of his partner, Dr. Mouledous, and haven't met Dr. Stewart at all. But I am acquainted with his staff. Nurse was very nice...but is the only nurse I have ever met that couldn't find a vein in my arm. I left with a very painful bruise.Receptionist just rubs me the wrong way and doesn't seem to have any organizational skills. She had me scheduled for the wrong doctor... "but that's ok, you can just come back on Friday..." Please, have a little more respect for my time!




